node.text: Bugs on your front end taking away at the overall look of your ride? Don’t use harsh cleaners that can damage or scratch your ride to remove them, use Bug & Tar Remover Wash! Bug & Tar Wash quickly breaks down bugs and tar to save exterior surfaces from permanent damage caused by corrosive insects and swirling and scratching caused by intense scrubbing during washing. Stay tuned until the end of the video to see these incredible results!

node.title: HOW TO REMOVE BUGS FROM YOUR RIDE!
